1. What are the basic actions of a mobile exploration?
Solution : A. Aggregation, grouping, filtering and visualization

2. Actions you can take from the Analytics mobile app include:
Solution : B. Saving Annotation and sharing snapshots of explorations

3. How do you focus your exploration on one aspect of a chart?
Solution : C. Tap a chart element, tap Drill In, and then select a dimension

4. While exploring, how do you go back to a previously used chart type?
Solution : D. Use the undo arrow in the upper right of the screen
